{184}{}{他被指控制造化学物质，这是匿名人士向警方报告的。在搜查过程中，警察发现了一些据称可用于制造毒品的物质。 -- That he was accused of producing chems - it was reported to the police by anonymous source. During the search the cops found some substance, which, allegedly, could be used for drug manufacturing.}
