{190}{}{那你在这里干什么？！去做你的工作吧！ -- What are you doing here then?! Go and do your job!}
#{191}{}{As you wish, mr. mayor.}
{191}{}{如你所愿，市长先生。 -- As you wish, mr. mayor.}
#{192}{}{I think so... Yes... Is there another Sam Phillips in the city?}
{192}{}{我认为是这样。。。对。。。城里还有萨姆・菲利普斯吗？ -- I think so... Yes... Is there another Sam Phillips in the city?}
