#{198}{}{I talked with one of the local "pushers". He said that Phillips didn't purchase any drugs or materials for producing them.}
{198}{}{我和当地的一个“推手”谈过。他说，菲利普斯没有购买任何药品或生产它们的材料。 -- I talked with one of the local "pushers". He said that Phillips didn't purchase any drugs or materials for producing them.}
#{199}{}{I still haven't managed to figure this out.}
{199}{}{我还没弄明白。 -- I still haven't managed to figure this out.}
